Name: El Taco Diablo
About the game: WARNING! This is NOT a game for the average player. Most players can’t survive more than 150 seconds in this Hardcore Competitive Stand-still Arena FPS. Your only goal is to survive as long as possible. It’s all about your accuracy and speed, there is no hand-holding. Compete on a global leaderboard and earn the #1 spot by killing endless waves of demonic Tacos and UFO’s. Discover a game that looks simple on the surface but hides a surprising amount of depth beneath its surface. Gameplay Features: Stylized Demonic Tacos Nextgen Taco Graphics Mariachi Inspired Rock Soundtrack 8 Different Enemies with Unique Abilities and Weaknesses 3 Weapons to Master
